name: Royal Crusaders of the Staff
description: Stumbling into lost treasure, the Royal Crusaders of the Staff used the wealth well and quickly rose in stature to local royalty. They also might haveâ€¦ killed their former house leader? And that worries some people? Maybe? Yikes. Stay away from these guys. Now consorting and aligning themselves with the Gibbun leadership, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
